This module is demo.workflow.core.linear.

To runLinear, produce. It performs io:
  
  workflow:
    step fetch:
      Return ok of Http.get("/orders").

    step persist:
      Let record be Sql.insert("orders", "payload").
      Return ok of record.

    compensate:
      Return ok of Secrets.rotate("orders-key").
  
    retry:
      max attempts: 3.
      backoff: exponential.
  
    timeout: 15 seconds.
  
  .
